      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"Well, those agitators are just stirring up trouble where there ain't none,\" one might grumble, swirling his coffee. \"We just need to make sure the folks know their place, you understand? Business can't run if everyone starts acting like they're equal.\" Another might nod grimly, \"It's just the way things have always been done down here; some things are just meant to stay put.\"",
